{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_52_02",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 2話 最高のバースデーライブ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バースデーライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—On the day of the birthday live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよだね！　私のバースデーライブ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s finally here! My birthday live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しかも、この日のために用意した衣装まで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’ve even got a special outfit prepared just for today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5999996503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.1999992689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "可愛いけど、大人っぽさもあって、凄くいいよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s cute‚ but also grown-up‚ and it looks amazing‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1999992689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-09.m4a",
      "text": "歳を一つ重ねて成長した私にピッタリだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s perfect for me‚ now that I’ve grown a year older!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9410835229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.1466660182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いつになくはしゃいでるな\nでも、本当によく似合ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re more excited than usual.\nBut it really suits you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-04.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6399992466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この場所も、この衣装も、頑張って用意してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For preparing this venue and this outfit with so much effort.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.266666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5266676109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-12.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実は少しだけ心残りがあってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ actually‚ I have a little regret.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5266676109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-05.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前に、今吐き出しちゃってもいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I let it out before the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0635051386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。今からでもどうにか出来ることなら\n俺がなんとかする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. If there’s anything that can be done even now‚\nI’ll handle it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333326977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9050058524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "私のマネージャーは優しいな～。でも、ちょっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My manager is so kind~. But‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9050058524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "難しいかも。……別に、いつものことなんだけどさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a bit difficult… though‚ it’s nothing new.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.9049980323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃をライブに誘ったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I invited Kotono to the live‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9049980323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "またフラれちゃったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but she turned me down again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6383361975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nでも、めげずに誘ってるの、俺は凄いと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nBut I think it’s amazing that you keep asking without giving up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1666633606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.4593506813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-02.m4a",
      "text": "諦められないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t give up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4593506813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-15.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルって凄いんだよ、って琴乃に伝えたいもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to show Kotono how amazing being an idol is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4260409355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "それに、出来れば琴乃にもお祝いしてほしかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if possible‚ I wanted Kotono to celebrate with me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4260409355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……なんてね。いつまでも引きずってられないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Just kidding. I can’t dwell on it forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4149308416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8593827248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-02.m4a",
      "text": "今はダメでも、この先何回だってライブをして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if not now‚ I’ll have many more lives in the future‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8593827248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-04.m4a",
      "text": "いつかは琴乃に、アイドルの私を見てもらおう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and someday Kotono will see me as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1260576725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.2127332372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "話してたら前向きになってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about it is making me feel positive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2127332372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-02.m4a",
      "text": "うん……もう、大丈夫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I’m okay now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がこれだけ頑張ってるんだ\nいつかきっと、妹さんに振り向いてもらえるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana’s working this hard…\nShe’ll surely notice you someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.392662271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-13.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね、なんてったって天才ちゃんだしね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. After all‚ I’m a genius!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.392662271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-03.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがと、{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thanks‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3989680687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4459947587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして。天才は関係ないけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re welcome. Genius or not doesn’t matter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4459947587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-05.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日は三枝さんも遙子ちゃんも観に来て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Saegusa-san and Haruko-chan are watching today too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0069449585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "くれてるんだよね。関係者席にはいなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though they weren’t in the staff seats.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9000111898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_02-koh006.m4a",
